               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Fluocinonide Cream USP, 0.05% (Emulsified Base) is supplied in 15 gram, 30 gram, and 60 gram tubes.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Fluocinonide Cream USP, 0.05% is supplied in 15 gram, 30 gram, and 60 gram tubes.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Fluocinonide Ointment USP, 0.05% is supplied in 15 gram, 30 gram, and 60 gram tubes.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20° to 25°C (68° to 77°F) [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Avoid excessive heat, above 40°C (104°F).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Manufactured In Croatia By:</paragraph>
